{"type":"message","id":"594c97fa","parentId":"f83121db","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:19:58.764Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 14:19 GMT+2] HOT RELOAD & HFT ARBITRAGE ANALYSIS.\n\n1.  **Hot Reload Implementation:**\n    *   Edit `src/agent_wrapper.py`: Add a background thread/task.\n    *   *Logic:* Check `os.path.getmtime(\"docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md\")`.\n    *   *Action:* If changed -> `reload_protocol()`. Log \"Hot Reload: Protocol Updated\".\n    *   *Verify:* Simulate a touch on `MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`.\n\n2.  **HFT Arbitrage Scan (DMarket Only):**\n    *   Use `dmarket_api.py` to fetch aggregated prices for high-volume items (AK-47 Redline, AWP Asiimov, Glock-18 Fade).\n    *   *Calculation:* `(Ask Price * 0.93) - Bid Price`.\n    *   *Constraint:* Find 5 items with >3% NET margin.\n    *   *Liquidity:* Check `sales_volume_24h` (if available via API or estimate).\n\n3.  **Steam Necessity Check:**\n    *   Compare DMarket price vs Steam Median Price.\n    *   *Hypothesis:* If DMarket is consistently -30% vs Steam, Steam is a \"ceiling\" but not a real-time signal. Removing Steam API calls = 2x speedup.\n\n4.  **Strategic Verdict:**\n    *   Can we make $100/mo with current bank? (Need ~$3000 volume/mo at 3% margin).\n    *   *Alternative:* Float/Pattern sniping (Blue Gem, Low Float).\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Hot Reload confirmation.\n    *   5 Arbitrage Opportunities (Item, Buy, Sell, Net %).\n    *   Steam Verdict (Keep/Kill).\n    *   Final Go/No-Go."}],"timestamp":1771157998762}}
