{"type":"message","id":"55f5ca5d","parentId":"53953697","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:22:17.725Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read_1771158137703_649","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿\"\"\"Market operations for DMarket API.\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom typing import Any\r\n\r\nfrom src.dmarket.api.client import GAME_MAP\r\nfrom src.dmarket.api_validator import validate_response\r\nfrom src.dmarket.schemas import MarketItemsResponse  # Updated v2.0 schema  # Updated v2.0 schema\r\n\r\n\r\nclass MarketMixin:\r\n    \"\"\"Methods for interacting with DMarket marketplace.\"\"\"\r\n\r\n    @validate_response(MarketItemsResponse, endpoint=\"/exchange/v1/market/items\")\r\n    async def get_market_items(\r\n        self,\r\n        game: str = \"csgo\",\r\n        limit: int = 100,\r\n        offset: int = 0,\r\n        currency: str = \"USD\",\r\n        price_from: float | None = None,\r\n        price_to: float | None = None,\r\n        title: str | None = None,\r\n        sort: str = \"price\",\r\n        force_refresh: bool = False,\r\n        tree_filters: str | None = None,\r\n        cursor: str = \"\",\r\n    ) -> dict[str, Any]:\r\n        game_id = GAME_MAP.get(game.lower(), game)\r\n        params = {\r\n            \"gameId\": game_id,\r\n            \"limit\": limit,\r\n            \"offset\": offset,\r\n            \"currency\": currency,\r\n        }\r\n        if cursor:\r\n            params[\"cursor\"] = cursor\r\n        if price_from is not None:\r\n            params[\"priceFrom\"] = str(int(price_from * 100))\r\n        if price_to is not None:\r\n            params[\"priceTo\"] = str(int(price_to * 100))\r\n        if title:\r\n            params[\"title\"] = title\r\n        if sort:\r\n            params[\"orderBy\"] = sort\r\n        if tree_filters:\r\n            params[\"treeFilters\"] = tree_filters\r\n\r\n        return await self._request(\"GET\", \"/exchange/v1/market/items\", params=params, force_refresh=force_refresh)\r\n\r\n    async def get_suggested_price(self, item_name: str, game: str = \"csgo\") -> float | None:\r\n        response = await self.get_market_items(game=game, title=item_name, limit=1)\r\n        items = response.get(\"objects\", response.get(\"items\", []))\r\n        if not items:\r\n            return None\r\n        suggested = items[0].get(\"suggestedPrice\")\r\n        if isinstance(suggested, dict):\r\n            return float(suggested.get(\"amount\", 0)) / 100\r\n        return float(suggested) / 100 if suggested else None\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771158137723}}
{"type":"message","id":"72d4d62d","parentId":"55f5ca5d","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:22:25.349Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Investigating Ask Prices**\n\nI'm currently focused on the `get_market_items` endpoint. It looks promising for retrieving the asking prices, crucial for calculating the desired metrics. I've confirmed that the endpoint provides \"Ask\" prices, which is a good starting point. Now, the plan is to move to the main task to gather prices and perform the calculations.\n\n\n**Searching for Bid Data**\n\nI'm now investigating how to acquire the \"Bid Price,\" the other critical component for calculations. The `get_user_targets` endpoint seems unhelpful, as it gets *my* targets, not the market's. I'm exploring the DMarket API source code, specifically `trading.py` and `extended.py`, hoping to find an endpoint to get market bid data. I will now search the API folder.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"I will search for the string \"targets\" within the `DMarket-Telegram-Bot-main/src/dmarket/api` directory to find methods for retrieving market targets.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771158145340_650","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"targets\" DMarket-Telegram-Bot-main/src/dmarket/api"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":14971,"output":301,"cacheRead":12072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15272,"cost":{"input":0.029942,"output":0.003612,"cacheRead":0.0024144,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0359684}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771158137726}}
